### =====================================================================
### Notification API  (base route: api/Notification/)  TagNotification: 999 Test
### =====================================================================
@host = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = your-dev-api-key
@token =

### Create
POST {{host}}/api/Notification/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "tags": [999]
}

### Read - all
POST {{host}}/api/Notification/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Read - by user
POST {{host}}/api/Notification/Read
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "pageSize": 20,
  "pageNumber": 1,
  "selectorArgs": {}
}

### Update
POST {{host}}/api/Notification/Update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "addTags": [999]
}

### Delete
POST {{host}}/api/Notification/Delete
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}
